name: Levia-Dragon - Daedalus (Rush)
desc:
[Requirement]: You can send 1 face-up "Umi" you control to the GY.
[Effect]: Destroy all other cards on the field.

name: Valkyrian Sewkyrie
desc: A servant of the gods who stitches and sews the way forward. She can illuminate the darkness.

name: Takriminos
desc: A member of a race of sea serpents that freely travels through the sea.

name: Gagaga Outfielder
desc: An enchanting baseball warrior overflowing with guts who excels at defense and unexpected batting. Known as the Magician of the Fence, he's the type who stays in your memory for things besides his records.

name: Achacha Catcher
desc: An enchanting baseball warrior with a clever lead and throws the ball like an arrow. He is called the keystone of the team, and is the type with a blazing playstyle who helps lead the way for his teammates.

name: Zubaba Batter
desc: An enchanting baseball warrior whose batting hits as hard as a punch. He is also called the squad captain, and he's the type to give it his all aggressively from the first pitch.

name: Psyphickupper
desc:
[Requirement]: During your Main Phase in which this card was Normal or Special Summoned, you can send the top card of your Deck to the GY.
[Effect]: This card loses 800 ATK until the end of this turn, then you can gain 800 LP.

name: Kimeluna the Lunar Dark Decider
desc:
[Requirement]: None
[Effect]: Choose up to 2 monsters your opponent controls, and change their battle positions. (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position.) Then, if you changed a battle position by this effect, you can choose 1 face-up monster you control, and change its battle position.

name: Viskam Nanotron
desc:
[Requirement]: If the only monsters in your GY are 3 monsters (Cyberse).
[Effect]: Add all monsters (Cyberse) from your GY to your hand, then place this card you control on the bottom of the Deck.

name: Gantry Dragon the Mythic Sword Heavenly Dragon
desc:
[Requirement]: If a face-up Field Spell is on the field.
[Effect]: Choose 1 "Build Dragon the Mythic Sword Dragon" in your GY, and Special Summon it to your field face-up. This turn, you cannot attack with monsters (non-Wyrm).

name: Dododo Second
desc:
[Requirement]: If a face-up "Hot-Blooded Spirits Stadium" is on the field, you can pay 500 LP.
[Effect]: This turn, if you would Tribute Summon a monster (FIRE) in Attack Position, you can treat this face-up card as 2 Tributes.

name: Gogogo Umpire
desc:
[Requirement]: You can shuffle 1 "Hot-Blooded Spirits Stadium" from your GY into the Deck.
[Effect]: Choose 1 Normal Monster (FIRE with 400 DEF) in your GY, and Special Summon it to your field face-up. This turn, you cannot attack with monsters (non-FIRE).

name: Uniform No. 99: Junior Baseball King Dragon, Home Groundra
desc:
[Requirement]: You can shuffle 3 monsters (FIRE) from your GY into the Deck.
[Effect]: Choose 1 "Uniform No. 39: Junior Baseball King, Home" in your GY, and Special Summon it to your field face-up, then this card gains 2000 ATK until the end of this turn.

name: Uniform No. 39: Junior Baseball King, Home
desc:
[Requirement]: If a face-up "Hot-Blooded Spirits Stadium" is on the field, you can send 2 face-up monsters (Level 4 FIRE) you control to the GY.
[Effect]: This card gains 2500 ATK until the end of this turn. This turn, you can only attack with this card.

name: CAN:D LIVE
desc:
"CAN:D" + "Psyphickupper"

[Requirement]: If your opponent controls a monster.
[Multi-Choice Effect]:
● Take 2000 damage, then you can make all face-up monsters your opponent currently controls lose 3000 ATK until the end of this turn.
● Gain 1000 LP, then you can choose 1 monster (Level 7 or higher Psychic) in your GY, and Special Summon it to your field face-up.

name: Yamiterasu the Divine Delayer
desc:
"Yamiruler the Dark Delayer" + "Valkyrian Sewkyrie"

[Requirement]: You can send the top card of your Deck to the GY.
[Multi-Choice Effect]:
● Until the end of your opponent's next turn, while this card is face-up, it gains 500 ATK, also neither player can Special Summon monsters (Level 9 or lower) in face-up Attack Position.
● Choose 1 monster on the field, and change its battle position.

name: Unbelievarmor
desc:
[Requirement]: Place 3 monsters (Level 7 or higher) with different Types from your GY on the top or bottom of the Deck in any order.
[Effect]: Choose 1 Normal Monster in your GY, and add it to your hand, then you can choose 1 face-up monster your opponent controls, and it loses 1500 ATK until the end of this turn.

name: Vanishing Torrent
desc:
[Requirement]: If you control a face-up monster (Sea Serpent).
[Effect]: Choose 1 Spell/Trap your opponent controls, and destroy it.

name: Hot-Blooded Spirits Stadium
desc:
[Requirement]: None
[Effect]: While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, all face-up monsters (FIRE) you control gain 400 ATK during your turn only, also all face-up monsters (FIRE) your opponent controls gain 400 ATK during their turn only.

name: Gagagaguts
desc:
[Requirement]: When a monster you control is destroyed by an opponent's card effect.
[Effect]: Choose 1 monster (FIRE) in your GY, and Special Summon it to your field in face-up Defense Position. Then, if you Special Summoned "Uniform No. 39: Junior Baseball King, Home" or "Uniform No. 99: Junior Baseball King Dragon, Home Groundra" by this effect, you can choose 1 monster your opponent controls, and destroy it.

name: Request 9
desc:
[Requirement]: When your monster is destroyed by an opponent's attack.
[Effect]: Gain 900 LP. Then, if you have 9 or more monsters (FIRE) in your GY, you can choose 1 "Uniform No. 39: Junior Baseball King, Home" or "Uniform No. 99: Junior Baseball King Dragon, Home Groundra" in your GY, and Special Summon it to your field face-up.

name: Kimeluna the Lunar Dark Decider
desc:
[Requirement]: None
[Effect]: Choose up to 2 monsters your opponent controls, and change their battle positions. (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position.) Then, if you changed a battle position by this effect, you can choose 1 face-up monster you control, and change its battle position.

name: The☆Star Dragon
desc:
[Requirement]: You can send the top card of your Deck to the GY.
[Effect]: This card loses 500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can choose 1 face-up monster your opponent controls, and it loses 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

name: Blue-Eyes White Dragon (Rush)
desc: This legendary dragon is a powerful engine of destruction. Virtually invincible, very few have faced this awesome creature and lived to tell the tale.

name: Sevens Road Enchanter
desc:
[Requirement]: You can send the top card of your Deck to the GY.
[Effect]: Choose 1 face-up monster (non-Level 3 Spellcaster) on the field, and return it to the hand. Then, if you returned "Sevens Road Magician" to the hand by this effect, you can draw 1 card.

name: Mirror Force (Rush)
desc:
[Requirement]: When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[Effect]: Destroy all Attack Position monsters your opponent controls.
